g.title: j198071508
g.text: Did you have family growing up?

g.title: j3040098323
g.text: Do you mean, did I have parents?

g.title: j397259863
g.text: No, I came from a test tube.

g.title: j1508703838
g.text: I meant more like siblings. Cousins. Etc.

g.title: j451027284
g.text: Oh. Not technically? But all us kids on the Zariman were basically raised together.

g.title: j2849862671
g.text: There's a reason I don't like the Man in the Wall.

g.title: j3187992996
g.text: I don't want to talk about it.

g.title: j1341293440
g.text: It... It wasn't pretty. Why're you asking?

g.title: j1512019948
g.text: Eleanor. She's driving me up the wall and I didn't know how much you'd understand.

g.title: j309009973
g.text: You know she and I are a "thing," right?

g.title: j179106865
g.text: She drives me nuts for a completely *different* reason. ;)

g.title: j3651737148
g.text: I'm not looking for gossip, mate. Or to start any nonsense.

g.title: j613596181
g.text: It's more about what she's not doing.

g.title: j2718713210
g.text: AUGH. No. No, no, no! She's my SISTER!

g.title: j3024785861
g.text: I'm just worried about her, is all.

g.title: j2467230366
g.text: There's an anniversary that we've...celebrated is the wrong word.

g.title: j2215514543
g.text: She can invade my mind any time...

g.title: j1268703979
g.text: And she missed it this year. She never does.

g.title: j3552416021
g.text: IN ALL THE NAMES OF SOL, STOP.

g.title: j271202900
g.text: This has been a... pretty messed up year, to be fair. Maybe she just forgot?

g.title: j2180030134
g.text: Can I ask what you were supposed to be commiserating?

g.title: j157631858
g.text: Have you just asked her about it?

g.title: j230823607
g.text: *Sigh.* You have a sick sense of humour, mate.

g.title: j2759024972
g.text: It's not really my story to tell, it's hers.

g.title: j3407986061
g.text: I was left on my own too much.

g.title: j1703238015
g.text: We lost someone who was important to both of us.

g.title: j4238055600
g.text: Then why're you bothering me? Go ask *her* what's up.

g.title: j2673702255
g.text: Anyway. About Eleanor? Whats she doing?

g.title: j158349
g.text: Have you talked to her about missing the date?

g.title: j118589665
g.text: Right. Well, now that I've managed to scrub my brain down with bleach, it's more about what she's not doing.

g.title: j3337368565
g.text: No. And I honestly couldn't tell you why. Instead, I'm here talking to you.

g.title: j1305991313
g.text: I assume whatever this event that you're commiserating was painful.

g.title: j443250487
g.text: Maybe now that everything in your lives have changed, you want to let it go? Maybe she does, too?

g.title: j789844985
g.text: Maybe. Maybe it is time to move on from the past. Which is ironic, considering your situation.

g.title: j3662936804
g.text: Eh, there's a difference between choosing to stay and being trapped. Trust me.

g.title: j1398442712
g.text: I like the view, what can I say?

g.title: j3224112310
g.text: Heh. Well. Thanks, all the same.

g.title: j227528949
g.text: You going to tell me what all this was about?

g.title: j2226099959
g.text: I will. Just... when I've had some time to think.
